#

Citrus Guacamole

10 min
$5.99
150 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-FreeNut-Free

Cuisine:

Mexican

Course:

Appetizer

Tags:

AppetizerSnackHealthy

Description

A vibrant and zesty twist on traditional guacamole with a refreshing citrus flavor.

Ingredients

  • ripe avocados: 2
  • lime juice: 2 tablespoons
  • orange juice: 1 tablespoon
  • red onion: 1/4 cup, finely chopped
  • tomato: 1, diced
  • cilantro: 2 tablespoons, chopped
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
